reviewText:
There is no question, this is the best video out on the tabernacle. You will learn more about the Tabernacle in the Wilderness in 50 min than a two year Bible College course. Not only that, you receive a free USA-ISRAEL Flag lapel with the words  "WE STAND WITH ISRAEL".  This kind of lapel would be very rare to find anywhere else.

YOU CAN ORDER A COPY AT WWW.HOPEOFISRAEL.NET
